    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯计划将4月份柴油海运出口量降至5个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/russia-plans-to-cut-diesel-export-by-sea-in-april-to-5-month-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在乌克兰无人机袭击炼油厂和季节性维护大幅降低原油加工率后，俄罗斯计划将 4 月份西方主要港口的每日柴油出口量降至五个月以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/russia-plans-to-cut-diesel-export-by-sea-in-april-to-5-month-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 09:50:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>风险资产出现任何下跌时迅速介入：汇丰银行的凯特纳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/jump-in-quickly-to-any-dip-in-risk-assets-hsbc-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰全球研究部首席多元资产策略师马克斯·凯特纳 (Max Ketner) 认为，市场将出现 2017 年风格的情景，投资者等待下跌，因为美国股市“仍将大幅上涨”。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/jump-in-quickly-to-any-dip-in-risk-assets-hsbc-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 09:46:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国将扩大 2025 年预算赤字，重新制定施舍计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/thailand-to-widen-2025-budget-deficit-as-it-reworks-handout-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级官员表示，泰国计划提高下一财年的财政赤字预估，以刺激低迷的经济，这是迄今为止最明确的信号，表明政府正转向通过国家预算为 140 亿美元的现金发放计划提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/thailand-to-widen-2025-budget-deficit-as-it-reworks-handout-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 09:38:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高利率影响需求，巴基斯坦通胀连续第三个月放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/pakistan-inflation-eases-a-third-month-as-high-rates-hit-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于创纪录的借贷成本削弱了经济增长和国内需求，巴基斯坦 3 月份的通胀率连续第三个月放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/pakistan-inflation-eases-a-third-month-as-high-rates-hit-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 09:13:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>反对派席卷土耳其地方选举后里拉下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/lira-dips-after-turkey-opposition-parties-sweep-local-elections-lugi5xc7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安领导的执政党在周日的地方选举中惨败，包括伊斯坦布尔和安卡拉在内的土耳其许多城市的控制权落入反对派手中，土耳其里拉走弱。信用违约掉期有所回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/lira-dips-after-turkey-opposition-parties-sweep-local-elections-lugi5xc7</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 05:21:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
